lus 通常比同等的 Game Pass 级别便宜。年度 PS Plus Essential 计划比一年的 Xbox Game Pass 便宜 52 美元，而相同时间段内的 12 个月 PS Plus Premium 会员资格比 Game Pass Ultimate 便宜 44 美元。</p><p>也就是说，微软在其所有第一方游戏发​​布后都会通过 Game Pass 提供访问权限，这是索尼无法比拟的诱人服务。 <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/xbox-game-pass-core-replaces-live-gold-on-september-14th-143904124.html">新的 Game Pass Core 等级</a>（取代 Xbox Live Gold）每年 60 美元，包括完整的在线多人游戏访问权限和 25 款游戏的初始库。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/sony-is-jacking-up-annual-playstation-plus-plans-by-as-much-as-40-164534502.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/sony-is-jacking-up-annual-playstation-plus-plans-by-as-much-as-40-164534502.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9e4fc9df-9093-41c2-bc2b-ce597a7899f3</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 30 Aug 2023 16:45:34 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693413765</ingested><modified> 2023-08-30T16:42:51+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="612" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-03/fc9c3040-af58-11ec-acef-b03391f10e42" width="1088"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="612" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-03/fc9c3040-af58-11ec-acef-b03391f10e42" width="1088"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Sony Interactive Entertainment]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[PlayStation Plus]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[PlayStation Plus]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Instagram reportedly making Reels longer to take on TikTok and YouTube]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>据<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/alex193a/status/1696865320705634488?s=46&amp;t=83RYMGD0s72VGeNSgmSBuQ">知名移动开发者兼泄密者 Alessandro Paluzzi 称，Instagram 似乎即将大幅增加 Reels 帖子的最大长度。</a>目前这些视频的硬性限制是三分钟，但 Paluzzi 提供的屏幕截图表明即将跃升至 10 分钟。这将有效地将社交媒体网站转变为像 YouTube 这样更强大的视频共享平台。</p><p>此举还将使 Meta 的 Instagram 能够进一步与竞争对手 TikTok 竞争，因为后者已经允许用户<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-time-limit-10-minutes-174130936.html">发布长达 10 分钟的视频。</a> TikTok 和 Instagram 似乎陷入了某种模仿的“衔尾蛇”，其中一个应用程序经常采用<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-adds-text-posts-to-compete-with-instagram-stories-161502542.html">另一个应用程序最初推出的</a><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/instagram-remix-any-video-tiktok-duet-152544191.html?src=rss">功能</a>。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>当 TikTok 和 Instagram 争夺长视频市场份额时，YouTube 正朝着相反的方向发展。它一直在努力在短视频领域获得更多份额， <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-is-adding-more-creator-tools-to-shorts-to-help-it-take-on-tiktok-160023789.html">最近添加了一套创作者工具</a>和一个<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-music-debuts-samples-a-tiktok-style-feed-for-music-discovery-160007555.html">类似 TikTok 的音乐发现源。</a>你可以轻松地将 Instagram 标记为“照片类”、将 TikTok 标记为“短视频类”、将 YouTube 标记为“长视频类”的日子已经一去不复返了。看起来他们都想成为“万事通”。</p><p> Engadget 联系 Meta，要求澄清有关向长视频内容发展的问题。该公司确认泄露的图像是真实的，但它们代表的是未经外部测试的“内部原型”。</p><p><strong>更新，美国东部时间 2023 年 8 月 30 日下午 1:36：</strong>本文已更新，包含来自 Meta 的声明。</p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/instagram-reportedly-making-reels-longer-to-take-on-tiktok-and-youtube-163059898.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/instagram-reportedly-making-reels-longer-to-take-on-tiktok-and-youtube-163059898.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 0eff2b71-c0f4-492f-9535-040249451948</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 30 Aug 2023 16:30:59 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693416894</ingested><modified> 2023-08-30T17:34:58+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Social & Online Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="3723" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/9e454ce0-4758-11ee-b7a7-bd94d2bd1e1b" width="5836"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3723" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/9e454ce0-4758-11ee-b7a7-bd94d2bd1e1b" width="5836"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[In this photo illustration an Instagram logo seen displayed on a smartphone screen in Chania, Greece on August 25, 2023.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[1623149150 - Instagram]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Google's Duet AI can generate emails and documents in different tones]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>谷歌透露了有关如何使用<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/googles-duet-ai-is-coming-to-workspace-apps-but-pro-users-will-need-to-pay-extra-150729432.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/googles-duet-ai-is-coming-to-workspace-apps-but-pro-users-will-need-to-pay-extra-150729432.html">Duet AI 助手</a>来帮助您快速处理电子邮件和文档<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://workspaceupdates.googleblog.com/2023/08/write-emails-documents-duetai-google-docs-gmail.html" data-original-link="https://workspaceupdates.googleblog.com/2023/08/write-emails-documents-duetai-google-docs-gmail.html">的更多详细信息</a>。在<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/gmail/" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/tag/gmail/">Gmail</a>中，该工具基于现有的人工智能功能（例如智能回复）而构建。单击或点击“帮助我写作”按钮，您将有多个选项可供选择。</p><p>选择“编写草稿”，您可以详细说明您希望<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:5;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/duet-ai/" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/tag/duet-ai/">Duet AI</a>生成的<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://support.google.com/mail/answer/13955415?visit_id=638284907496284760-1950408489&amp;p=duet-help-me-write&amp;rd=1" data-original-link="https://support.google.com/mail/answer/13955415?visit_id=638284907496284760-1950408489&amp;p=duet-help-me-write&amp;rd=1">消息类型</a>。谷歌表示，该工具将能够从线程中以前的消息中提取信息，使草稿回复更加相关。如果 Duet AI 以可能过于随意的语气创建消息，您可以要求助手将其变得更正式。有一些选项可以使草稿更加详细或简洁，如果你喜欢冒险，你可以选择“我感觉很幸运”选项。谷歌表示，这将“为您起草的内容引入有趣的语气和风格变化”。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:6;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/google-docs/" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/tag/google-docs/">Google Docs</a>中的选项非常相似，不过如果您愿意，您<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:7;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://support.google.com/docs/answer/13951448?visit_id=638290077545746450-2042367713&amp;p=duet-help-me-write&amp;rd=1" data-original-link="https://support.google.com/docs/answer/13951448?visit_id=638290077545746450-2042367713&amp;p=duet-help-me-write&amp;rd=1">可以</a>使 Duet AI 的语气更加随意。有一些选项可以生成部分或整个文档的摘要、使用要点（对于那些<em>Axios</em>粉丝）以及根据您的初始描述创建不同的草稿。此外，谷歌表示您可以使用自定义指令来“优化生成的内容”。文档的“帮我写”工具可以引入<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:8;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-docs-dropdown-menu-feature-announced-162857231.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/google-docs-dropdown-menu-feature-announced-162857231.html">智能画布功能</a>。</p><p>目前，新的虚拟助手仅适用于每位用户每月额外支付 30 美元购买 Duet AI for Google Workspace Enterprise 附加组件的组织。 Duet AI 将在未来几个月内面向中小型企业以及消费者推出，但谷歌尚未透露定价。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/googles-duet-ai-can-generate-emails-and-documents-in- Different-tones-161534645.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/googles-duet-ai-can-generate-emails-and-documents-in-different-tones-161534645.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> aa60727c-efe8-49fa-9847-2d21dbba5d8e</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 30 Aug 2023 16:15:34 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693411601</ingested><modified> 2023-08-30T16:06:44+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2592" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.